d":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:47:36.000Z","msg":"2018年仲講鋼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架車愈硬個人愈傷啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409f2799cb0aa36e34e6da742261006330be7ddc","tid":518823,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T20:53:35.000Z","msg":"40萬夠唔夠出volvo v60"},{"pid":"2e02569416280604736ef3c8f12af6afa9e11269","tid":518823,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T21:55:16.000Z","msg":"日本車襟揸丫嘛，整又平<br />\n歐洲車新車冇得頂，舊車冇得整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650daf73d51f0be9a6d694d4965e7a30af678ddf","tid":518823,"uid":105366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T22:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>toyota prius 都講緊係33萬 <br />\n加多少少 , 40萬都有benz cla<br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺benz cla 都幾抵玩  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncla垃撚圾</blockquote>用黎溝女</blockquote><br />\n啲女都知CLA係冇錢又要充大頭先買。<br />\n睇車嚟秤人既女亦唔會睇得起呢部車。</blockquote>新車45萬都叫冇錢,你又渣緊乜?</blockquote><br />\n我係冇錢但唔會充大頭鬼囉。(而且唔係Benz fans)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>要買乜先唔係充大頭鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買golf又係唔係充大頭鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要平又要買歐洲車</blockquote><br />\n邊個話你知買Golf係充大頭鬼？<br />\nVW一直標榜係人民之車。<br />\n係有啲人自己個先入為主concept錯左。<br />\n以前舊甲蟲舊Mini都係歐洲車，但冇人話呢啲平價歐洲車係充大頭鬼喎。<br />\n<br />\n但CLA呢，就真正係充大頭鬼既代表車。"},{"pid":"213a2ee80d86c6725defcb7480c9b820bb28661e","tid":518823,"uid":105366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T22:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2018年仲講鋼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架車愈硬個人愈傷啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭尾撞就係既。<br />\n但講俾人T-Bone既話，依然係有分別。"},{"pid":"04729a42cda682422050abecdbe2ddaf45d06152","tid":518823,"uid":123177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:36:06.000Z","msg":"講硬淨，其實日本車得出口果堆好d （跟歐洲crash test既）<br />\n本土款/水貨車就算吧啦，人地冇無限速公路，大眾要求輕巧/省油<br />\n<br />\n同埋歐洲車個車架同避震 真係硬淨得來又舒服好多<br />\n日本車一味軟....<br />\n呢樣一渣上手就感覺到 冇得呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁當然要計埋整就係另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ce683a55f6354641667ea158b26bcde504210a","tid":518823,"uid":123177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:38:04.000Z","msg":"我指既硬淨係札實既感覺，過坑/入灣<br />\nFeel到坐左響一件過既野度 ，日本車feel唔到個車架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}